<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    .otp-container {
      background-color: #F3F4F6;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      color: #4F46E5;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6B7280;
      margin-top: 32px;
      border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
      padding-top: 16px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Your ticket has been attended to!</h2>
  
  <p>You can confirm it your issue has been resolved, if not you can get back to us.</p>
  
  <div class="otp-container">
    <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
  </div>


  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; {{year}} Rooli. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>